These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, writing
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pineapple
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, thriller
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person eating nectarine is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | writing       | traveling |
| Food         | pineapple | nectarine  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller       | crime      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, grapefruit
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, august
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Food      | grapefruit     | cabbage |
| Job           | entrepreneur | lawyer      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Birthday         | october | august     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, golf
House: townhouse, victorian
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the victorian house is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Sport          | handball    | golf   |
| House   | victorian  | townhouse   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, blend
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
2 different pets are kept: turtle, bird
1. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
3. the blend-smoker is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Cigar      | fonseca       | blend |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Job           | security-guard | nurse    |
| Pet   | turtle           | bird   |

 #################################

 
