1. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person playing domino is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| City           | colone  | san-francisco   |
| Game   | domino  | go      |
| Sport         | climbing | volleyball |
| Transport     | taxi     | snowmobile |

